<head>IN VAIN</head>
    <list type="translations">
        <item xml:lang="zh">徒然</item>
    </list>
<div type="definition">
<p>FAILING to ACHIEVE any AIMS.</p>
    </div>
<div type="notes">
<div type="modern-chinese-criteria">
<p>白 is a current word for doing something in vain (also: at no cost)</p>
<p>白白 is intensitive.</p>
<p>徒 is a literary way of referring to something being in vain.</p>
<p>乾 is colloquial for "to no purpose"</p>
<p>無效 refers to an action being to no effect.</p>
<p>虛 as in 不虛此行 "the trip has not been in vain".</p>
<p>rough draft to BEGIN TO identify synonym group members for analysis, based on CL etc. 18.11.2003. CH ／</p>
        </div>
    </div>
